msgid "A tool to convert RAW images to DNG container"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບປ່ຽນຮູບພາບ RAW ເປັນ DNG container"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttodng/converttodngplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Generic tool can convert RAW images data to DNG format.</para><para>The Digital Negative is "
"a lossless RAW image format created by Adobe.</para><para>See details about this format from <link "
"url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_Negative'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມືທົ່ວໄປນີ້ສາມາດປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນຮູບພາບ RAW ເປັນຮູບແບບ DNG ໄດ້.</para><para>Digital Negative ແມ່ນຮູບແບບຮູບພາບ RAW ແບບ lossless ທີ່ສ້າງໂດຍ Adobe.</para><para>ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບຮູບແບບນີ້ຈາກ <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_Negative'>ໜ້ານີ້</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttoheif/converttoheifplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To HEIF"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນເປັນ HEIF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttoheif/converttoheifplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to HEIF format"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບປ່ຽນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ HEIF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttoheif/converttoheifplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to HEIF format.</para><para>High "
"Efficiency Image File Format (HEIF), also known as High Efficiency Image Coding (HEIC), is a file "
"format for individual images and image sequences. It was developed by the Moving Picture Experts Group "
"(MPEG) and it claims that twice as much information can be stored in a HEIF image as in a JPEG image "
"of the same size, resulting in a better quality image. HEIF also supports animation, and is capable of "
"storing more information than an animated GIF at a small fraction of the size.</para><para>See <link "
"url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/High_Efficiency_Image_File_Format'>High Efficiency Image File "
"Format</link> for details.</para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມື Batch Queue Manager ນີ້ສາມາດປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ HEIF ໄດ້.</para><para>High Efficiency Image File Format (HEIF) ຫຼື ຮູ້ຈັກກັນໃນນາມ High Efficiency Image Coding (HEIC), ແມ່ນຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ສຳລັບຮູບພາບດ່ຽວ ແລະ ລຳດັບຮູບພາບ. ມັນຖືກພັດທະນາໂດຍ Moving Picture Experts Group (MPEG) ແລະ ອ້າງວ່າສາມາດເກັບຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້ສອງເທົ່າໃນຮູບພາບ HEIF ເມື່ອທຽບກັບຮູບພາບ JPEG ທີ່ມີຂະໜາດເທົ່າກັນ, ສົ່ງຜົນໃຫ້ໄດ້ຮູບພາບທີ່ມີຄຸນນະພາບດີກວ່າ. HEIF ຍັງຮອງຮັບພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວ ແລະ ສາມາດເກັບຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້ຫຼາຍກວ່າ GIF ເຄື່ອນໄຫວໃນຂະໜາດທີ່ນ້ອຍກວ່າ.</para><para>ເບິ່ງ <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/High_Efficiency_Image_File_Format'>High Efficiency Image File Format</link> ສຳລັບລາຍລະອຽດ.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojp2/converttojp2plugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To JP2"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນເປັນ JP2"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojp2/converttojp2plugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to JPEG-2000 format"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບປ່ຽນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ JPEG-2000"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojp2/converttojp2plugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to JPEG-2000 format.</para><para>This is "
"an image compression standard and coding system. It was created by the Joint Photographic Experts "
"Group committee in 2000 with the intention of superseding their original discrete cosine transform-"
"based JPEG standard (created in 1992) with a newly designed, wavelet-based method.</para><para>See "
"details about this format from <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_2000'>this page</link>.</"
"para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມື Batch Queue Manager ນີ້ສາມາດປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ JPEG-2000 ໄດ້.</para><para>ນີ້ແມ່ນມາດຕະຖານການບີບອັດຮູບພາບ ແລະ ລະບົບການເຂົ້າລະຫັດ. ມັນຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍຄະນະກຳມະການ Joint Photographic Experts Group ໃນປີ 2000 ດ້ວຍຄວາມຕັ້ງໃຈທີ່ຈະປ່ຽນແທນມາດຕະຖານ JPEG ເດີມ (ສ້າງໃນປີ 1992) ດ້ວຍວິທີການທີ່ອອກແບບໃໝ່ໂດຍໃຊ້ wavelet.</para><para>ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບຮູບແບບນີ້ຈາກ <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_2000'>ໜ້ານີ້</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojpeg/converttojpegplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To JPEG"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນເປັນ JPEG"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojpeg/converttojpegplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to JPEG format"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບປ່ຽນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ JPEG"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojpeg/converttojpegplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to JPEG format.</para><para>The Joint "
"Photographic Experts Group format is a commonly used method of lossy compression for digital images, "
"particularly for those images produced by digital photography.</para><para>See details about this "
"format from <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມື Batch Queue Manager ນີ້ສາມາດປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ JPEG ໄດ້.</para><para>ຮູບແບບ Joint Photographic Experts Group ແມ່ນວິທີການທີ່ນິຍົມໃຊ້ໃນການບີບອັດແບບ lossy ສຳລັບຮູບພາບດິຈິຕອນ, ໂດຍສະເພາະຮູບພາບທີ່ໄດ້ຈາກການຖ່າຍຮູບດິຈິຕອນ.</para><para>ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບຮູບແບບນີ້ຈາກ <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG'>ໜ້ານີ້</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojxl/converttojxlplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To JXL"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນເປັນ JXL"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojxl/converttojxlplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to JXL format"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບປ່ຽນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ JXL"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojxl/converttojxlplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to JPEG-XL format.</para><para>JPEG-XL is "
"a royalty-free raster-graphics file format that supports both lossy and lossless compression. It is "
"designed to outperform existing raster formats and thus to become their universal replacement.</"
"para><para>See details about this format from <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_XL'>this "
"page</link>.</para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມື Batch Queue Manager ນີ້ສາມາດປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ JPEG-XL ໄດ້.</para><para>JPEG-XL ແມ່ນຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ກຣາບຟິກ raster ແບບບໍ່ມີຄ່າລິຂະສິດ ທີ່ຮອງຮັບທັງການບີບອັດແບບ lossy ແລະ lossless. ມັນຖືກອອກແບບມາໃຫ້ມີປະສິດທິພາບເໜືອກວ່າຮູບແບບ raster ທີ່ມີຢູ່ ແລະ ກາຍເປັນຕົວແທນສາກົນ.</para><para>ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບຮູບແບບນີ້ຈາກ <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_XL'>ໜ້ານີ້</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopgf/converttopgfplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To PGF"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນເປັນ PGF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopgf/converttopgfplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to PGF format"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບປ່ຽນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ PGF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopgf/converttopgfplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to PGF format.</para><para>The Progressive "
"Graphics File is a wavelet-based bitmapped image format that employs lossless and lossy data "
"compression.</para><para>See details about this format from <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Progressive_Graphics_File'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມື Batch Queue Manager ນີ້ສາມາດປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ PGF ໄດ້.</para><para>Progressive Graphics File ແມ່ນຮູບແບບຮູບພາບ bitmap ທີ່ໃຊ້ wavelet ເຊິ່ງໃຊ້ການບີບອັດຂໍ້ມູນແບບ lossless ແລະ lossy.</para><para>ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບຮູບແບບນີ້ຈາກ <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Progressive_Graphics_File'>ໜ້ານີ້</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopng/converttopng.cpp:54
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>If conversion to PNG fails, this may be due to the color profile check. Simply insert the tool for "
"color profile conversion before this tool and select the desired color profile.</b>"
msgstr "<b>ຖ້າການປ່ຽນເປັນ PNG ລົ້ມເຫຼວ, ອາດຈະເປັນຍ້ອນການກວດສອບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ສີ. ພຽງແຕ່ໃສ່ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບການປ່ຽນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ສີກ່ອນເຄື່ອງມືນີ້ ແລະ ເລືອກໂປຣໄຟລ໌ສີທີ່ຕ້ອງການ.</b>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopng/converttopngplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To PNG"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນເປັນ PNG"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopng/converttopngplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to PNG format"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບປ່ຽນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ PNG"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopng/converttopngplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to PNG format.</para><para>The Portable "
"Network Graphics is a raster-graphics file-format that supports lossless data compression.</"
"para><para>See details about this format from <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Portable_Network_Graphics'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມື Batch Queue Manager ນີ້ສາມາດປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ PNG ໄດ້.</para><para>Portable Network Graphics ແມ່ນຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ກຣາບຟິກ raster ທີ່ຮອງຮັບການບີບອັດຂໍ້ມູນແບບ lossless.</para><para>ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບຮູບແບບນີ້ຈາກ <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portable_Network_Graphics'>ໜ້ານີ້</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttotiff/converttotiffplugin.cpp:42
