msgstr "ປ່ຽນເປັນ TIFF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttotiff/converttotiffplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to TIFF format"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບປ່ຽນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ TIFF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttotiff/converttotiffplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to TIFF format.</para><para>The Tagged "
"Image File Format is a computer file format for storing raster graphics images, popular among graphic "
"artists, the publishing industry, and photographers.</para><para>See details about this format from "
"<link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TIFF'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມື Batch Queue Manager ນີ້ສາມາດປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ TIFF ໄດ້.</para><para>Tagged Image File Format ແມ່ນຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ຄອມພິວເຕີສຳລັບເກັບຮູບພາບກຣາບຟິກ raster, ເປັນທີ່ນິຍົມໃນໝູ່ນັກສິລະປະ, ອຸດສາຫະກຳການພິມ ແລະ ຊ່າງຖ່າຍຮູບ.</para><para>ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບຮູບແບບນີ້ຈາກ <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TIFF'>ໜ້ານີ້</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttowebp/converttowebpplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To WEBP"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນເປັນ WEBP"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttowebp/converttowebpplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to WEBP format"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບປ່ຽນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ WEBP"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttowebp/converttowebpplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to WEBP format.</para><para>WEBP is an "
"image file format that Google has developed as a replacement for JPEG, PNG, and GIF file formats. WEBP "
"yields files that are smaller for the same quality, or of higher quality for the same size. It "
"supports both lossy and lossless compression, as well as animation and alpha transparency.</"
"para><para>See details about this format from <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WebP'>this "
"page</link>.</para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມື Batch Queue Manager ນີ້ສາມາດປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນຮູບພາບເປັນຮູບແບບ WEBP ໄດ້.</para><para>WEBP ແມ່ນຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ຮູບພາບທີ່ Google ພັດທະນາຂຶ້ນເພື່ອປ່ຽນແທນຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ JPEG, PNG ແລະ GIF. WEBP ໃຫ້ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຂະໜາດນ້ອຍກວ່າສຳລັບຄຸນນະພາບດຽວກັນ, ຫຼື ຄຸນນະພາບສູງກວ່າສຳລັບຂະໜາດດຽວກັນ. ມັນຮອງຮັບທັງການບີບອັດແບບ lossy ແລະ lossless, ລວມທັງພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວ ແລະ alpha transparency.</para><para>ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດກ່ຽວກັບຮູບແບບນີ້ຈາກ <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WebP'>ໜ້ານີ້</link>.</para>"

