#: core/dplugins/bqm/custom/userscript/userscriptplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can run user shell script as workflow stage.</para><para>Script "
"variables:</para><para>Uses <b>$INPUT</b> and <b>$OUTPUT</b> for input / output filenames (with "
"special characters escaped). These would be substituted before shell execution.</para><para>Uses "
"<b>$TITLE</b>, <b>$COMMENTS</b>, <b>$COLORLABEL</b>, <b>$PICKLABEL</b>, <b>$RATING</b> and "
"<b>$TAGSPATH</b> to handle digiKam properties.</para>"
msgstr "<para>ເຄື່ອງມື Batch Queue Manager ນີ້ສາມາດລັນ shell script ຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້ເປັນຂັ້ນຕອນການເຮັດວຽກໄດ້.</para><para>ຕົວແປສະຄຣິບ:</para><para>ໃຊ້ <b>$INPUT</b> ແລະ <b>$OUTPUT</b> ສຳລັບຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຂາເຂົ້າ / ຂາອອກ (ພ້ອມ escape ຕົວອັກສອນພິເສດ). ສິ່ງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ກ່ອນການດຳເນີນການ shell.</para><para>ໃຊ້ <b>$TITLE</b>, <b>$COMMENTS</b>, <b>$COLORLABEL</b>, <b>$PICKLABEL</b>, <b>$RATING</b> ແລະ <b>$TAGSPATH</b> ເພື່ອຈັດການຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງ digiKam.</para>"

