msgid ""
"<para>This plugin allows users to load and save image using Libtiff codec.</para><para>Tagged Image "
"File Format, abbreviated TIFF or TIF, is a computer file format for storing raster graphics images, "
"popular among graphic artists, the publishing industry, and photographers. TIFF is widely supported by "
"scanning, faxing, word processing, optical character recognition, image manipulation, desktop "
