msgstr "ລະບຸຂະໜາດຂອງແປງຖາສີທີ່ໃຊ້ແຕ້ມໜ້າກາກຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:286
#, kde-format
msgid "Norm of brightness gradient"
msgstr "ມາດຖານຂອງການໄລ່ລະດັບຄວາມແຈ້ງ"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:287
#, kde-format
msgid "Sum of absolute values of brightness gradients"
msgstr "ຜົນບວກຂອງຄ່າສຳບູນຂອງການໄລ່ລະດັບຄວາມແຈ້ງ"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:288
#, kde-format
msgid "Absolute value of brightness gradient"
msgstr "ຄ່າສຳບູນຂອງການໄລ່ລະດັບຄວາມແຈ້ງ"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:289
#, kde-format
msgid "Norm of luma gradient"
msgstr "ມາດຖານຂອງການໄລ່ລະດັບແສງ (Luma)"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:290
#, kde-format
msgid "Sum of absolute values of luma gradients"
msgstr "ຜົນບວກຂອງຄ່າສຳບູນຂອງການໄລ່ລະດັບແສງ (Luma)"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:291
#, kde-format
msgid "Absolute value of luma gradient"
msgstr "ຄ່າສຳບູນຂອງການໄລ່ລະດັບແສງ (Luma)"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:294
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to choose a gradient function. This function is used to determine which pixels "
"should be removed or kept."
msgstr "ທາງເລືອກນີ້ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ທ່ານເລືອກຟັງຊັນການໄລ່ລະດັບສີ. ຟັງຊັນນີ້ໃຊ້ເພື່ອກຳນົດວ່າພິກເຊວໃດຄວນຖືກລຶບອອກ ຫຼື ເກັບໄວ້."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:297
#, kde-format
msgid "Preserve Skin Tones"
msgstr "ຮັກສາໂທນສີຜິວ"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:298
#, kde-format
msgid "Enable this option to preserve pixels whose color is close to a skin tone."
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ທາງເລືອກນີ້ເພື່ອຮັກສາພິກເຊວທີ່ມີສີໃກ້ຄຽງກັບໂທນສີຜິວ."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:312
#, kde-format
msgid "Overall rigidity of the seams:"
msgstr "ຄວາມແຂງໂດຍລວມຂອງຮອຍຕໍ່:"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:316
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Use this value to give a negative bias to the seams which are not straight. May be useful to prevent "
"distortions in some situations, or to avoid artifacts from pixel skipping (it is better to use low "
"values in such case). This setting applies to the whole selected layer if no rigidity mask is used. "
"Note: the bias is proportional to the difference in the transversal coordinate between each two "
"successive points, elevated to the power of 1.5, and summed up for the whole seam."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຄ່ານີ້ເພື່ອໃຫ້ອະຄະຕິທາງລົບກັບຮອຍຕໍ່ທີ່ບໍ່ຊື່. ອາດຈະເປັນປະໂຫຍດໃນການປ້ອງກັນການບິດເບືອນໃນບາງສະຖານະການ, ຫຼື ເພື່ອຫຼີກເວັ້ນເສດທີ່ເກີດຈາກການຂ້າມພິກເຊວ (ມັນດີກວ່າທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ຄ່າຕໍ່າໃນກໍລະນີດັ່ງກ່າວ). ການຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ໃຊ້ກັບຊັ້ນທີ່ເລືອກທັງໝົດຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ໜ້າກາກຄວາມແຂງ. ໝາຍເຫດ: ອະຄະຕິແມ່ນເປັນອັດຕາສ່ວນກັບຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງໃນພິກັດຂວາງລະຫວ່າງແຕ່ລະສອງຈຸດທີ່ຕໍ່ເນື່ອງກັນ, ຍົກກຳລັງ 1.5, ແລະ ລວມເຂົ້າກັນສຳລັບຮອຍຕໍ່ທັງໝົດ."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:325
#, kde-format
msgid "Maximum number of transversal steps:"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນສູງສຸດຂອງຂັ້ນຕອນທາງຂວາງ:"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:329
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you choose the maximum transversal step that the pixels in the seams can take. In the "
"standard algorithm, corresponding to the default value step = 1, each pixel in a seam can be shifted "
"by at most one pixel with respect to its neighbors. This implies that the seams can form an angle of "
"at most 45 degrees with respect to their base line. Increasing the step value lets you overcome this "
"limit, but may lead to the introduction of artifacts. In order to balance the situation, you can use "
"the rigidity setting."
msgstr "ທາງເລືອກນີ້ໃຫ້ທ່ານເລືອກຂັ້ນຕອນທາງຂວາງສູງສຸດທີ່ພິກເຊວໃນຮອຍຕໍ່ສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້. ໃນ algorithm ມາດຕະຖານ, ທີ່ສອດຄ່ອງກັບຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ step = 1, ແຕ່ລະພິກເຊວໃນຮອຍຕໍ່ສາມາດຖືກຍ້າຍໄດ້ຢ່າງຫຼາຍໜຶ່ງພິກເຊວທຽບກັບພິກເຊວຂ້າງຄຽງ. ນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າຮອຍຕໍ່ສາມາດສ້າງມຸມໄດ້ສູງສຸດ 45 ອົງສາທຽບກັບເສັ້ນພື້ນຖານຂອງພວກມັນ. ການເພີ່ມຄ່າຂັ້ນຕອນຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເອົາຊະນະຂໍ້ຈຳກັດນີ້, ແຕ່ອາດຈະນຳໄປສູ່ການເກີດມີເສດພາບທີ່ບໍ່ຕ້ອງການ. ເພື່ອປັບສົມດຸນສະຖານະການ, ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວາມແຂງໄດ້."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:339
#, kde-format
msgid "Side switch frequency:"
msgstr "ຄວາມຖີ່ຂອງການສະຫຼັບດ້ານ:"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:343
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"During the carving process, at each step the optimal seam to be carved is chosen based on the "
"relevance value for each pixel. However, in the case where two seams are equivalent (which may happen, "
"for instance, when large portions of the image have the same color), the algorithm always chooses the "
"seams from one side.  In some cases, this can pose problems, e.g. an object centered in the original "
"image might not be centered in the resulting image. In order to overcome this effect, this setting "
"allows the favored side to be switched automatically during rescaling, at the cost of slightly worse "
"performance."
msgstr "ໃນລະຫວ່າງຂະບວນການຄວັດ, ໃນແຕ່ລະຂັ້ນຕອນ ຮອຍຕໍ່ທີ່ເໝາະສົມທີ່ສຸດທີ່ຈະຖືກຄວັດອອກຈະຖືກເລືອກໂດຍອີງໃສ່ຄ່າຄວາມກ່ຽວຂ້ອງສຳລັບແຕ່ລະພິກເຊວ. ຢ່າງໃດກໍຕາມ, ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ສອງຮອຍຕໍ່ມີຄວາມເທົ່າທຽມກັນ (ເຊິ່ງອາດຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນ, ຕົວຢ່າງ, ເມື່ອສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ຂອງຮູບມີສີດຽວກັນ), algorithm ຈະເລືອກຮອຍຕໍ່ຈາກດ້ານດຽວສະເໝີ. ໃນບາງກໍລະນີ, ສິ່ງນີ້ສາມາດເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດບັນຫາ, ເຊັ່ນ: ວັດຖຸທີ່ຢູ່ເຄິ່ງກາງໃນຮູບຕົ້ນສະບັບອາດຈະບໍ່ຢູ່ເຄິ່ງກາງໃນຮູບທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບ. ເພື່ອເອົາຊະນະຜົນກະທົບນີ້, ການຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ດ້ານທີ່ນິຍົມຖືກສະຫຼັບອັດຕະໂນມັດໃນລະຫວ່າງການປັບຂະໜາດ, ໂດຍແລກກັບປະສິດທິພາບທີ່ຫຼຸດລົງເລັກນ້ອຍ."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:355
#, kde-format
msgid "Resize Order:"
msgstr "ລຳດັບການປັບຂະໜາດ:"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:357
#, kde-format
msgid "Horizontally first"
msgstr "ທາງຂວາງກ່ອນ"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:358
#, kde-format
msgid "Vertically first"
msgstr "ທາງຕັ້ງກ່ອນ"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:360
#, kde-format
msgid "Here you can set whether to resize horizontally first or vertically first."
msgstr "ຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດວ່າຈະປັບຂະໜາດທາງຂວາງກ່ອນ ຫຼື ທາງຕັ້ງກ່ອນ."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:378
#, kde-format
msgid "Target size"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດເປົ້າໝາຍ"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:381
#, kde-format
