msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືແກ້ໄຂເມຕາເດຕາຂອງລາຍການ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/metadata/metadataedit/metadataeditplugin.cpp:64
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"This tool allows users to changes plenty of metadata from items.<br><br>Most common Exif, Iptc, and "
"Xmp tags used in photography are listed for editing with standardized values.<br><br>For photo "
"agencies, pre-configured subjects can be used to describe the items contents based on Iptc reference "
"codes."
