#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check Enfuse setting"
msgid "Automatic Local/Global Image Features Balance (Levels)"
msgstr "ປັບສົມດຸນຄຸນລັກສະນະຮູບພາບ ທ້ອງຖິ່ນ/ທົ່ວໄປ ອັດຕະໂນມັດ (Levels)"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:111
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Optimize image features (contrast, saturation, . . .) to be as global as possible."
msgstr "ປັບປຸງຄຸນລັກສະນະຂອງຮູບພາບ (ຄວາມຕັດກັນ, ຄວາມອີ່ມຕົວຂອງສີ, . . .) ໃຫ້ເປັນແບບທົ່ວໄປທີ່ສຸດເທົ່າທີ່ຈະເປັນໄປໄດ້."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:113
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Set automatic level selection (maximized) for pyramid blending, i.e. optimize image features "
"(contrast, saturation, . . .) to be as global as possible."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າການເລືອກລະດັບອັດຕະໂນມັດ (ສູງສຸດ) ສຳລັບການປະສົມແບບ pyramid, ເຊັ່ນ: ປັບປຸງຄຸນລັກສະນະຂອງຮູບພາບ "
"(ຄວາມຕັດກັນ, ຄວາມອີ່ມຕົວຂອງສີ, . . .) ໃຫ້ເປັນແບບທົ່ວໄປທີ່ສຸດເທົ່າທີ່ຈະເປັນໄປໄດ້."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:116
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider Enfuse settings"
msgid "Image Features Balance:"
msgstr "ຄວາມສົມດຸນຄຸນລັກສະນະຮູບພາບ:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:121
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Balances between local features (small number) or global features (high number)."
msgstr "ຄວາມສົມດຸນລະຫວ່າງຄຸນລັກສະນະທ້ອງຖິ່ນ (ຈຳນວນໜ້ອຍ) ຫຼື ຄຸນລັກສະນະທົ່ວໄປ (ຈຳນວນຫຼາຍ)."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:123
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Set the number of levels for pyramid blending. Balances towards local features (small number) or "
"global features (high number). Additionally, a low number trades off quality of results for faster "
"execution time and lower memory usage."
msgstr ""
"ກຳນົດຈຳນວນລະດັບສຳລັບການປະສົມແບບ pyramid. ປັບສົມດຸນໄປທາງຄຸນລັກສະນະທ້ອງຖິ່ນ (ຈຳນວນໜ້ອຍ) ຫຼື "
"ຄຸນລັກສະນະທົ່ວໄປ (ຈຳນວນຫຼາຍ). ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ຈຳນວນທີ່ຕ່ຳຈະແລກປ່ຽນຄຸນນະພາບຂອງຜົນໄດ້ຮັບກັບເວລາປະມວນຜົນທີ່ໄວຂຶ້ນ "
"ແລະ ການນຳໃຊ້ໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳທີ່ຕ່ຳກວ່າ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:128
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Hard Mask"
msgstr "Hard Mask"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:130
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Useful only for focus stack to improve sharpness."
msgstr "ມີປະໂຫຍດສະເພາະສຳລັບ focus stack ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຄວາມແຈ້ງ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:132
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Force hard blend masks without averaging on finest scale. This is only useful for focus stacks with "
"thin and high contrast features. It improves sharpness at the expense of increased noise."
msgstr ""
"ບັງຄັບໃຊ້ hard blend masks ໂດຍບໍ່ມີການສະເລ່ຍໃນຂະໜາດທີ່ລະອຽດທີ່ສຸດ. ອັນນີ້ມີປະໂຫຍດພຽງແຕ່ສຳລັບ focus stacks "
"ທີ່ມີຄຸນລັກສະນະບາງ ແລະ ມີຄວາມຕັດກັນສູງ. ມັນຊ່ວຍປັບປຸງຄວາມແຈ້ງແຕ່ຈະເພີ່ມ noise ຂຶ້ນ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:137
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider Enfuse settings"
msgid "Well-Exposedness Contribution:"
msgstr "ການປະກອບສ່ວນຂອງການຮັບແສງທີ່ດີ:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:142
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Contribution of well exposed pixels to the blending process."
msgstr "ການປະກອບສ່ວນຂອງພິກເຊວທີ່ມີການຮັບແສງດີໃນຂະບວນການປະສົມ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:144
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Set the well-exposedness criterion contribution for the blending process. Higher values will favor "
"well-exposed pixels."
msgstr ""
"ກຳນົດເກນການປະກອບສ່ວນຂອງການຮັບແສງທີ່ດີສຳລັບຂະບວນການປະສົມ. ຄ່າທີ່ສູງກວ່າຈະເອື້ອອຳນວຍໃຫ້ກັບພິກເຊວທີ່ມີການຮັບແສງດີ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:147
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider enfuse settings"
msgid "High-Saturation Contribution:"
msgstr "ການປະກອບສ່ວນຂອງຄວາມອີ່ມຕົວສູງ:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:153
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Contribution of highly saturated pixels to the blending process."
msgstr "ການປະກອບສ່ວນຂອງພິກເຊວທີ່ມີຄວາມອີ່ມຕົວສູງໃນຂະບວນການປະສົມ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:155
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid "Increasing this value makes pixels with high saturation contribute more to the final output."
msgstr "ການເພີ່ມຄ່ານີ້ເຮັດໃຫ້ພິກເຊວທີ່ມີຄວາມອີ່ມຕົວສູງປະກອບສ່ວນຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນໃນຜົນໄດ້ຮັບສຸດທ້າຍ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:158
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider enfuse settings"
msgid "High-Contrast Contribution:"
msgstr "ການປະກອບສ່ວນຂອງຄວາມຕັດກັນສູງ:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:164
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Contribution of highly contrasted pixels to the blending process."
msgstr "ການປະກອບສ່ວນຂອງພິກເຊວທີ່ມີຄວາມຕັດກັນສູງໃນຂະບວນການປະສົມ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:166
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Sets the relative weight of high-contrast pixels. Increasing this weight makes pixels with neighboring "
"differently colored pixels contribute more to the final output. Particularly useful for focus stacks."
msgstr ""
"ກຳນົດນ້ຳໜັກຂອງພິກເຊວທີ່ມີຄວາມຕັດກັນສູງ. ການເພີ່ມນ້ຳໜັກນີ້ເຮັດໃຫ້ພິກເຊວທີ່ມີເພື່ອນບ້ານສີຕ່າງກັນ "
"ປະກອບສ່ວນຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນໃນຜົນໄດ້ຮັບສຸດທ້າຍ. ເປັນປະໂຫຍດໂດຍສະເພາະສຳລັບ focus stacks."

