#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/mjpegstream/mjpegstreamdlg_views.cpp:233
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid ""
"A transition is a visual effect applied between two images. For some effects, the duration can depend "
"on random values and can change while the stream is playing."
