msgid "Selects a JPEG output with 90% compression rate (lossy compression, smaller size)."
msgstr "ເລືອກຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ JPEG ທີ່ມີອັດຕາການບີບອັດ 90% (ການບີບອັດແບບສູນເສຍ, ຂະໜາດນ້ອຍກວ່າ)."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panointropage.cpp:163
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"JPEG output\": Using JPEG output, the panorama file will be smaller at the cost of information loss "
"during compression. This is the easiest way to share the result, or print it online or in a shop."
msgstr ""
"\"ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ JPEG\": ການໃຊ້ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ JPEG, ໄຟລ໌ພາໂນຣາມາຈະນ້ອຍລົງແລກກັບການສູນເສຍຂໍ້ມູນໃນລະຫວ່າງການບີບອັດ. "
"ນີ້ແມ່ນວິທີທີ່ງ່າຍທີ່ສຸດໃນການແບ່ງປັນຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ, ຫຼື ພິມອອນໄລນ໌ ຫຼື ຢູ່ຮ້ານ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panointropage.cpp:169
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option: radio"
msgid "TIFF output"
msgstr "ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ TIFF"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panointropage.cpp:170
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: tooltip"
msgid "Selects a TIFF output compressed using the LZW algorithm (lossless compression, bigger size)."
msgstr "ເລືອກຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ TIFF ທີ່ບີບອັດໂດຍໃຊ້ algorithm LZW (ການບີບອັດແບບບໍ່ສູນເສຍ, ຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່ກວ່າ)."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panointropage.cpp:172
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"TIFF output\": Using TIFF output, you get the same color depth as your original photos using RAW "
"images at the cost of a bigger panorama file."
msgstr ""
"\"ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ TIFF\": ການໃຊ້ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ TIFF, ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບຄວາມເລິກຂອງສີເທົ່າກັບຮູບພາບຕົ້ນສະບັບຂອງທ່ານທີ່ໃຊ້ຮູບພາບ "
"RAW ແລກກັບໄຟລ໌ພາໂນຣາມາທີ່ໃຫຍ່ກວ່າ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panoitemspage.cpp:52
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "Set Panorama Images"
msgstr "ກຳນົດຮູບພາບພາໂນຣາມາ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panoitemspage.cpp:66
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Set here the list of your images to blend into a panorama. Please follow these conditions:"
msgstr "ກຳນົດລາຍການຮູບພາບຂອງທ່ານທີ່ຈະປະສົມເປັນພາໂນຣາມາຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້. ກະລຸນາປະຕິບັດຕາມເງື່ອນໄຂເຫຼົ່ານີ້:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panoitemspage.cpp:67
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Images are taken from the same point of view."
msgstr "ຮູບພາບຖືກຖ່າຍຈາກຈຸດດຽວກັນ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panoitemspage.cpp:68
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Images are taken with the same camera (and lens)."
msgstr "ຮູບພາບຖືກຖ່າຍດ້ວຍກ້ອງດຽວກັນ (ແລະ ເລນ)."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panoitemspage.cpp:70
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Note that, in the case of a 360° panorama, the first image in the list will be the image that will be "
"in the center of the panorama."
msgstr "ໝາຍເຫດວ່າ, ໃນກໍລະນີຂອງພາໂນຣາມາ 360°, ຮູບທຳອິດໃນລາຍການຈະເປັນຮູບທີ່ຈະຢູ່ເຄິ່ງກາງຂອງພາໂນຣາມາ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:68
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "Panorama Stitched"
msgstr "ຕໍ່ພາບພາໂນຣາມາແລ້ວ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:84
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າການບັນທຶກ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:88
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:textbox"
msgid "File name template:"
msgstr "ແມ່ແບບຊື່ໄຟລ໌:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:92
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Name of the panorama file (without its extension)."
msgstr "ຊື່ຂອງໄຟລ໌ພາໂນຣາມາ (ບໍ່ມີນາມສະກຸນ)."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:93
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"File name template\": Set here the base name of the files that will be saved. For example, if your "
"template is \"panorama\" and if you chose a JPEG output, then your panorama will be saved with the "
"name \"panorama.jpg\". If you choose to save also the project file, it will have the name "
"\"panorama.pto\"."
msgstr ""
"\"ແມ່ແບບຊື່ໄຟລ໌\": ກຳນົດຊື່ພື້ນຖານຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຈະບັນທຶກຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້. ຕົວຢ່າງ, ຖ້າແມ່ແບບຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນ \"panorama\" "
"ແລະ ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ JPEG, ພາໂນຣາມາຂອງທ່ານຈະຖືກບັນທຶກດ້ວຍຊື່ \"panorama.jpg\". "
"ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການນຳ, ມັນຈະມີຊື່ \"panorama.pto\"."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:100
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Save project file"
msgstr "ບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:102
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Save the project file for further processing within Hugin GUI."
msgstr "ບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການສຳລັບການປະມວນຜົນເພີ່ມເຕີມພາຍໃນ Hugin GUI."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:103
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"Save project file\": You can keep the project file generated to stitch your panorama for further "
"tweaking within %1 by checking this. This is useful if you want a different projection, modify the "
"horizon or the center of the panorama, or modify the control points to get better results."
msgstr ""
"\"ບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການ\": ທ່ານສາມາດເກັບໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນເພື່ອຕໍ່ພາໂນຣາມາຂອງທ່ານສຳລັບການປັບແຕ່ງເພີ່ມເຕີມພາຍໃນ %1 "
"ໂດຍການກວດສອບສິ່ງນີ້. ນີ້ເປັນປະໂຫຍດຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການ projection ທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ, ດັດແກ້ເສັ້ນຂອບຟ້າ ຫຼື "
"ຈຸດໃຈກາງຂອງພາໂນຣາມາ, ຫຼື ດັດແກ້ຈຸດຄວບຄຸມເພື່ອໃຫ້ໄດ້ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບທີ່ດີກວ່າ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:208
#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:217
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title: dialog"
msgid "Warning"
msgstr "ຄຳເຕືອນ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:209
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "This file already exists"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ນີ້ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:218
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "One or more converted raw files already exists (they will be skipped during the copying process)"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ raw ທີ່ແປງແລ້ວໜຶ່ງ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍໄຟລ໌ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ (ພວກມັນຈະຖືກຂ້າມໃນລະຫວ່າງຂະບວນການສຳເນົາ)"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:263
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Panorama Stitching is Done"
msgstr "ການຕໍ່ພາບພາໂນຣາມາສຳເລັດແລ້ວ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:264
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Congratulations. Your images are stitched into a panorama."
msgstr "ຂໍສະແດງຄວາມຍິນດີ. ຮູບພາບຂອງທ່ານຖືກຕໍ່ເປັນພາໂນຣາມາແລ້ວ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:265
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Your panorama will be created to the directory:"
msgstr "ພາໂນຣາມາຂອງທ່ານຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນໂຟນເດີ:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:267
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "once you press the \"Finish\" button, with the name set below."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານກົດປຸ່ມ \"ສຳເລັດ\", ດ້ວຍຊື່ທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ຂ້າງລຸ່ມນີ້."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:268
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"If you choose to save the project file, and if your images were raw images then the converted images "
"used during the stitching process will be copied at the same time (those are TIFF files that can be "
"big)."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກທີ່ຈະບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການ, ແລະ ຖ້າຮູບພາບຂອງທ່ານເປັນຮູບພາບ raw, ຮູບພາບທີ່ແປງແລ້ວທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນຂະບວນການຕໍ່ພາບ "
"ຈະຖືກສຳເນົາໄປພ້ອມກັນ (ເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ TIFF ທີ່ສາມາດມີຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່)."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:297
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Error"
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:83
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title: window"
msgid "Optimization"
msgstr "ການປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:97
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option: check"
msgid "Level horizon"
msgstr "ປັບລະດັບເສັ້ນຂອບຟ້າ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: tooltip"
msgid "Detect the horizon and adapt the project to make it horizontal."
msgstr "ກວດຈັບເສັ້ນຂອບຟ້າ ແລະ ປັບໂຄງການເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ມັນເປັນແນວນອນ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:100
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"Level horizon\": Detect the horizon and adapt the projection so that the detected horizon is an "
"horizontal line in the final panorama"
msgstr ""
"\"ປັບລະດັບເສັ້ນຂອບຟ້າ\": ກວດຈັບເສັ້ນຂອບຟ້າ ແລະ ປັບ projection ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເສັ້ນຂອບຟ້າທີ່ກວດພົບເປັນເສັ້ນແນວນອນ "
"ໃນພາໂນຣາມາສຸດທ້າຍ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:171
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Optimization is in progress, please wait."
msgstr "ການປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບກຳລັງດຳເນີນການ, ກະລຸນາລໍຖ້າ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:205
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "The optimization step according to your settings is ready to be performed."
msgstr "ຂັ້ນຕອນການປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບຕາມການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງທ່ານພ້ອມທີ່ຈະດຳເນີນການແລ້ວ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:206
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"This step can include an automatic leveling of the horizon, and also an automatic projection selection "
"and size."
msgstr "ຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້ສາມາດລວມມີການປັບລະດັບເສັ້ນຂອບຟ້າອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ແລະ ການເລືອກ projection ແລະ ຂະໜາດອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:208
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "To perform this operation, the \"%1\" program will be used."
msgstr "ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການນີ້, ໂປຣແກຣມ \"%1\" ຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:210
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Press the \"Next\" button to run the optimization."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມ \"ຖັດໄປ\" ເພື່ອແລ່ນການປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:310
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Optimization has failed."
msgstr "ການປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບລົ້ມເຫຼວ."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:85
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title: window"
msgid "Pre-Processing Images"
msgstr "ການປະມວນຜົນຮູບພາບເບື້ອງຕົ້ນ"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option: check"
msgid "Detect moving skies"
msgstr "ກວດຈັບທ້ອງຟ້າທີ່ເຄື່ອນທີ່"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:101
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: tooltip"
msgid ""
"Automatic detection of clouds to prevent wrong keypoints matching between images due to moving clouds."
msgstr "ການກວດຈັບເມກອັດຕະໂນມັດເພື່ອປ້ອງກັນການຈັບຄູ່ keypoints ທີ່ຜິດພາດລະຫວ່າງຮູບພາບເນື່ອງຈາກເມກທີ່ເຄື່ອນທີ່."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:103
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"Detect moving skies\": During the control points selection and matching, this option discards any "
"points that are associated to a possible cloud. This is useful to prevent moving clouds from altering "
"the control points matching process."
msgstr ""
