#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/printcreator/wizard/advprintintropage.cpp:72
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<qt><p><h1><b>Welcome to Print Creator</b></h1></p><p>This assistant will guide you to assemble images "
"to be printed following specific templates as Photo Album, Photo Collage, or Framed Photo.</p><p>An "
"adaptive photo collection page layout can be also used, based on Atkins algorithm.</p></qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt><p><h1><b>ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບສູ່ ຜູ້ສ້າງການພິມ</b></h1></p><p>ຜູ້ຊ່ວຍນີ້ຈະນຳພາທ່ານໃນການລວບລວມຮູບພາບ "
"ທີ່ຈະພິມຕາມແມ່ແບບສະເພາະ ເຊັ່ນ ອັນບັ້ມຮູບ, ຮູບຕັດຕໍ່, ຫຼື ຮູບໃສ່ກອບ.</p><p>"
"ສາມາດໃຊ້ໂຄງຮ່າງໜ້າລວບລວມຮູບແບບປັບຕົວໄດ້, ໂດຍອີງໃສ່ algorithm ຂອງ Atkins.</p></qt>"

