#: core/libs/dimg/filters/bw/mixersettings.cpp:144
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Enable this option if you want preserve the image luminosity."
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການຮັກສາຄວາມສະຫວ່າງຂອງຮູບພາບ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/bw/mixersettings.cpp:149
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option: color"
msgid "Monochrome"
msgstr "Monochrome"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/bw/mixersettings.cpp:151
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: help"
msgid ""
"Use \"Monochrome\" mode to convert color picture to Black and White.\n"
"The \"red channel\" modifies the contrast of photograph.\n"
"The \"green channel\" enhances or reduces the details level of photograph.\n"
"The \"blue channel\" affects the noise of photograph.\n"
"Note: in this mode, the histogram will display only luminosity values."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ໂຫມດ \"Monochrome\" ເພື່ອແປງຮູບພາບສີເປັນຂາວດຳ.\n"
"\"ຊ່ອງສີແດງ\" ດັດແປງຄວາມຄົມຊັດຂອງຮູບຖ່າຍ.\n"
"\"ຊ່ອງສີຂຽວ\" ປັບປຸງ ຫຼື ຫຼຸດລະດັບລາຍລະອຽດຂອງຮູບຖ່າຍ.\n"
"\"ຊ່ອງສີຟ້າ\" ມີຜົນຕໍ່ນອຍສ໌ຂອງຮູບຖ່າຍ.\n"
"ໝາຍເຫດ: ໃນໂຫມດນີ້, ຮິສໂຕແກຣມຈະສະແດງສະເພາະຄ່າຄວາມສະຫວ່າງເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/bw/mixersettings.cpp:311
