#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/lensfunsettings.cpp:65
#, kde-format
msgid "Chromatic Aberration"
msgstr "ຄວາມຄາດເຄື່ອນຂອງສີ (Chromatic Aberration)"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/lensfunsettings.cpp:66
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Chromatic aberration is easily recognized as color fringes towards the image corners. CA is due to a "
"varying lens focus for different colors."
msgstr "ຄວາມຄາດເຄື່ອນຂອງສີສາມາດສັງເກດເຫັນໄດ້ງ່າຍເປັນແຖບສີທີ່ມຸມຂອງຮູບ. CA ເກີດມາຈາກການໂຟກັສຂອງເລນທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນສຳລັບແຕ່ລະສີ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/lensfunsettings.cpp:69
#, kde-format
msgid "Vignetting"
msgstr "ຂອບມືດ (Vignetting)"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/lensfunsettings.cpp:70
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Vignetting refers to an image darkening, mostly in the corners. Optical and natural vignetting can be "
"canceled out with this option, whereas mechanical vignetting will not be cured."
msgstr "Vignetting ໝາຍເຖິງການທີ່ຮູບມືດລົງ ໂດຍສະເພາະຢູ່ມຸມພາບ. ການເກີດຂອບມືດແບບ Optical ແລະ ແບບທຳມະຊາດສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ດ້ວຍຕົວເລືອກນີ້, ແຕ່ການເກີດຂອບມືດແບບກົນຈັກຈະບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/lensfunsettings.cpp:73
#, kde-format
msgid "Distortion"
msgstr "ການບິດເບືອນ"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/lensfunsettings.cpp:74
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Distortion refers to an image deformation, which is most pronounced towards the corners. These Seidel "
"aberrations are known as pincushion and barrel distortions."
msgstr "ການບິດເບືອນໝາຍເຖິງການຜິດຮູບຂອງພາບ, ເຊິ່ງເຫັນໄດ້ຊັດເຈນທີ່ສຸດຢູ່ບໍລິເວນມຸມ. ຄວາມຜິດປົກກະຕິ Seidel ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເອີ້ນວ່າ ການບິດເບືອນແບບ pincushion ແລະ barrel."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/lensfunsettings.cpp:77
#, kde-format
msgid "Geometry"
msgstr "ເລຂາຄະນິດ"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/lensfunsettings.cpp:78
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Four geometries are handled here: Rectilinear (99 percent of all lenses), Fisheye, Cylindrical, "
"Equirectangular."
msgstr "ຮອງຮັບເລຂາຄະນິດ 4 ຮູບແບບ: Rectilinear (99 ເປີເຊັນຂອງເລນທັງໝົດ), Fisheye, Cylindrical, Equirectangular."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/lensfunsettings.cpp:80
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>Note: lens correction options depend of filters available in LensFun library. See <a href='http://"
"lensfun.sourceforge.net'>LensFun project web site</a> for more information.</b>"
msgstr "<b>ໝາຍເຫດ: ຕົວເລືອກການແກ້ໄຂເລນແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບຟິວເຕີທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນໄລບຣາຣີ LensFun. ເບິ່ງ <a href='http://lensfun.sourceforge.net'>ເວັບໄຊໂຄງການ LensFun</a> ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ.</b>"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/levels/histogrambox.cpp:68
#, kde-format
msgid "Channel:"
msgstr "ຊ່ອງ:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/levels/histogrambox.cpp:74
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Select the histogram scale.</p><p>If the image's maximal counts are small, you can use the "
"<b>linear</b> scale.</p><p><b>Logarithmic</b> scale can be used when the maximal counts are big; if it "
"is used, all values (small and large) will be visible on the graph.</p>"
msgstr "<p>ເລືອກມາດຕາສ່ວນຂອງຮິສໂຕແກຣມ.</p><p>ຖ້າຈຳນວນສູງສຸດຂອງຮູບມີໜ້ອຍ, ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ <b>Linear</b> ໄດ້.</p><p><b>Logarithmic</b> ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ເມື່ອຈຳນວນນັບສູງສຸດມີຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່; ຖ້າໃຊ້ມັນ, ຄ່າທັງໝົດ (ນ້ອຍ ແລະ ໃຫຍ່) ຈະສະແດງຢູ່ໃນກຣາບ.</p>"

