#: core/libs/dimg/filters/nr/nrsettings.cpp:85
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>Threshold</b>: Adjusts the threshold for denoising of the image in a range from 0.0 (none) to 10.0. "
"The threshold is the value below which everything is considered noise."
msgstr "<b>ເກນ (Threshold)</b>: ປັບເກນສຳລັບການລົບສັນຍານລົບກວນຂອງຮູບ ໃນຊ່ວງ 0.0 (ບໍ່ມີ) ຫາ 10.0. ເກນແມ່ນຄ່າທີ່ຕ່ຳກວ່ານັ້ນຈະຖືກຖືວ່າເປັນສັນຍານລົບກວນທັງໝົດ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/nr/nrsettings.cpp:89
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>Softness</b>: This adjusts the softness of the thresholding (soft as opposed to hard thresholding). "
"The higher the softness the more noise remains in the image."
msgstr "<b>ຄວາມນຸ່ມນວນ</b>: ນີ້ແມ່ນການປັບຄວາມນຸ່ມນວນຂອງການຕັດເກນ. ຍິ່ງຄວາມນຸ່ມນວນສູງເທົ່າໃດ ສັນຍານລົບກວນກໍຈະຍັງເຫຼືອຢູ່ໃນຮູບຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/nr/nrsettings.cpp:95
#, kde-format
msgid "Estimate Noise"
msgstr "ປະເມີນສັນຍານລົບກວນ"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/nr/nrsettings.cpp:96
#, kde-format
