#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:114
#, kde-format
msgid "Unsharp mask"
msgstr "Unsharp mask"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:123
#, kde-format
msgid "Select the sharpening method to apply to the image."
msgstr "ເລືອກວິທີການເພີ່ມຄວາມຄົມຊັດທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ກັບຮູບ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:144
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A sharpness of 0 has no effect, 1 and above determine the sharpen matrix radius that determines how "
"much to sharpen the image."
msgstr "ຄວາມຄົມຊັດ 0 ຈະບໍ່ມີຜົນຫຍັງ, 1 ແລະ ສູງກວ່າ ແມ່ນການກຳນົດລັດສະໝີຂອງເມທຣິກຄວາມຄົມຊັດ ເຊິ່ງກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ຮູບຄົມຊັດຫຼາຍປານໃດ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:161
#, kde-format
msgid "Radius:"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີ:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:166
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Radius value is the Gaussian blur matrix radius value used to determines how much to blur the image."
msgstr "ຄ່າລັດສະໝີແມ່ນຄ່າລັດສະໝີຂອງເມທຣິກ Gaussian blur ທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ຮູບມົວຫຼາຍປານໃດ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:174
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The value of the difference between the original and the blur image that is added back into the "
"original."
msgstr "ຄ່າຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງລະຫວ່າງຮູບຕົ້ນສະບັບ ແລະ ຮູບທີ່ມົວ ທີ່ຈະຖືກເພີ່ມກັບເຂົ້າໄປໃນຮູບຕົ້ນສະບັບ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:182
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The threshold, as a fraction of the maximum luminosity value, needed to apply the difference amount."
msgstr "ເກນ (Threshold), ເຊິ່ງເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງຄ່າຄວາມສະຫວ່າງສູງສຸດ, ທີ່ຈຳເປັນໃນການນຳໃຊ້ຈຳນວນຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:186
#, kde-format
msgid "Suppress color noise."
msgstr "ຫຼຸດສັນຍານລົບກວນສີ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:188
#, kde-format
msgid "An option to apply filter on luminosity channel only used to suppress chroma noise amplification."
msgstr "ຕົວເລືອກເພື່ອໃຊ້ຟິວເຕີກັບຊ່ອງຄວາມສະຫວ່າງເທົ່ານັ້ນ ເພື່ອຫຼຸດການຂະຫຍາຍຕົວຂອງສັນຍານລົບກວນສີ (Chroma noise)."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:211
#, kde-format
msgid "Circular sharpness:"
msgstr "ຄວາມຄົມຊັດແບບວົງກົມ:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:216
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This is the radius of the circular convolution. It is the most important parameter for using this "
"tool. For most images the default value of 1.0 should give good results. Select a higher value when "
"your image is very blurred."
msgstr "ນີ້ແມ່ນລັດສະໝີຂອງການ Convolution ແບບວົງກົມ. ມັນເປັນພາຣາມິເຕີທີ່ສຳຄັນທີ່ສຸດສຳລັບການໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງມືນີ້. ສຳລັບຮູບສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ 1.0 ຈະໃຫ້ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບທີ່ດີ. ເລືອກຄ່າທີ່ສູງກວ່າເມື່ອຮູບຂອງທ່ານມົວຫຼາຍ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:220
#, kde-format
msgid "Correlation:"
msgstr "ຄວາມສຳພັນ (Correlation):"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:225
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Increasing the correlation may help to reduce artifacts. The correlation can range from 0-1. Useful "
"values are 0.5 and values close to 1, e.g. 0.95 and 0.99. Using a high value for the correlation will "
"reduce the sharpening effect of the tool."
msgstr "ການເພີ່ມຄວາມສຳພັນອາດຈະຊ່ວຍຫຼຸດສິ່ງແປກປອມ (Artifacts) ໄດ້. ຄວາມສຳພັນສາມາດຢູ່ລະຫວ່າງ 0-1. ຄ່າທີ່ເປັນປະໂຫຍດຄື 0.5 ແລະ ຄ່າທີ່ໃກ້ຄຽງ 1, ເຊັ່ນ: 0.95 ແລະ 0.99. ການໃຊ້ຄ່າຄວາມສຳພັນສູງຈະຫຼຸດຜົນຂອງການເຮັດໃຫ້ພາບຄົມຊັດລົງ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:230
#, kde-format
msgid "Noise filter:"
msgstr "ຟິວເຕີສັນຍານລົບກວນ:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:235
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Increasing the noise filter parameter may help to reduce artifacts. The noise filter can range from "
"0-1 but values higher than 0.1 are rarely helpful. When the noise filter value is too low, e.g. 0.0 "
"the image quality will be very poor. A useful value is 0.01. Using a high value for the noise filter "
"will reduce the sharpening effect of the tool."
msgstr "ການເພີ່ມພາຣາມິເຕີຟິວເຕີສັນຍານລົບກວນອາດຈະຊ່ວຍຫຼຸດສິ່ງແປກປອມໄດ້. ຟິວເຕີສັນຍານລົບກວນສາມາດຢູ່ລະຫວ່າງ 0-1 ແຕ່ຄ່າທີ່ສູງກວ່າ 0.1 ບໍ່ຄ່ອຍມີປະໂຫຍດ. ເມື່ອຄ່າຟິວເຕີສັນຍານລົບກວນຕ່ຳເກີນໄປ, ເຊັ່ນ 0.0 ຄຸນນະພາບຂອງຮູບຈະບໍ່ດີຫຼາຍ. ຄ່າທີ່ເປັນປະໂຫຍດຄື 0.01. ການໃຊ້ຄ່າສູງສຳລັບຟິວເຕີສັນຍານລົບກວນຈະຫຼຸດຜົນຂອງການເຮັດໃຫ້ພາບຄົມຊັດລົງ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:241
#, kde-format
msgid "Gaussian sharpness:"
msgstr "ຄວາມຄົມຊັດແບບ Gaussian:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:246
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This is the sharpness for the Gaussian convolution. Use this parameter when your blurring is of a "
"Gaussian type. In most cases you should set this parameter to 0, because it causes nasty artifacts. "
"When you use non-zero values, you will probably also have to increase the correlation and/or noise "
"filter parameters."
msgstr "ນີ້ແມ່ນຄວາມຄົມຊັດສຳລັບ Gaussian convolution. ໃຊ້ພາຣາມິເຕີນີ້ເມື່ອຄວາມມົວຂອງທ່ານເປັນແບບ Gaussian. ໃນກໍລະນີສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ ທ່ານຄວນຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ເປັນ 0, ເພາະມັນອາດຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດສິ່ງແປກປອມທີ່ບໍ່ດີ. ເມື່ອທ່ານໃຊ້ຄ່າທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນສູນ, ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງເພີ່ມຄ່າ correlation ແລະ/ຫຼື ຟິວເຕີສັນຍານລົບກວນນຳ."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:251
#, kde-format
msgid "Matrix size:"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ Matrix:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:255
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This parameter determines the size of the transformation matrix. Increasing the matrix width may give "
"better results, especially when you have chosen large values for circular or Gaussian sharpness."
msgstr "ພາຣາມິເຕີນີ້ກຳນົດຂະໜາດຂອງ Transformation matrix. ການເພີ່ມຄວາມກວ້າງຂອງ matrix ອາດຈະໃຫ້ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບທີ່ດີກວ່າ, ໂດຍສະເພາະເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກຄ່າທີ່ໃຫຍ່ສຳລັບຄວາມຄົມຊັດແບບວົງກົມ ຫຼື Gaussian."

