msgstr "FBDD"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:510
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Noise Reduction</title><para>Select here the noise reduction method to apply during RAW "
"decoding.</para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>None</emphasis>: no noise reduction.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Wavelets</emphasis>: wavelets correction to erase noise while "
"preserving real detail. It is applied after interpolation.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>FBDD</"
"emphasis>: Fake Before Demosaicing Denoising noise reduction. It is applied before interpolation.</"
"item></list></para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>ການຫຼຸດສຽງລົບກວນ</title><para>ເລືອກວິທີການຫຼຸດສຽງລົບກວນຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້ເພື່ອໃຊ້ໃນລະຫວ່າງການຖອດລະຫັດ RAW.</"
"para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>None</emphasis>: ບໍ່ມີການຫຼຸດສຽງລົບກວນ.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Wavelets</emphasis>: ການແກ້ໄຂ wavelets ເພື່ອລຶບສຽງລົບກວນ "
"ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຮັກສາລາຍລະອຽດຕົວຈິງ. ມັນຖືກໃຊ້ຫຼັງຈາກການແຊກຄ່າ.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>FBDD</"
"emphasis>: ການຫຼຸດສຽງລົບກວນ FBDD (Fake Before Demosaicing Denoising). ມັນຖືກໃຊ້ກ່ອນການແຊກຄ່າ.</"
"item></list></para>"

