#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:571
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Workspace</title><para>Select here the output color space used to decode RAW data.</"
"para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>Raw (linear)</emphasis>: in this mode, no output color "
"space is used during RAW decoding.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>sRGB</emphasis>: this is an RGB "
"color space, created cooperatively by Hewlett-Packard and Microsoft. It is the best choice for images "
"destined for the Web and portrait photography.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Adobe RGB</"
"emphasis>: this color space is an extended RGB color space, developed by Adobe. It is used for "
"photography applications such as advertising and fine art.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Wide "
"Gamut</emphasis>: this color space is an expanded version of the Adobe RGB color space.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Pro-Photo</emphasis>: this color space is an RGB color space, "
"developed by Kodak, that offers an especially large gamut designed for use with photographic outputs "
"in mind.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Custom</emphasis>: use a custom output color space "
"profile.</item></list></para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>ພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກ</title><para>ເລືອກພື້ນທີ່ສີຜົນລັດທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອຖອດລະຫັດຂໍ້ມູນ RAW ຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້.</"
"para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>Raw (linear)</emphasis>: ໃນໂໝດນີ້, ບໍ່ມີພື້ນທີ່ສີຜົນລັດ "
"ຖືກໃຊ້ໃນລະຫວ່າງການຖອດລະຫັດ RAW.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>sRGB</emphasis>: ນີ້ແມ່ນພື້ນທີ່ສີ RGB, "
"ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍການຮ່ວມມືຂອງ HP ແລະ Microsoft. ມັນເປັນທາງເລືອກທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດສຳລັບຮູບພາບທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນເວັບ ແລະ ການຖ່າຍຮູບຄົນ.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Adobe RGB</"
"emphasis>: ພື້ນທີ່ສີນີ້ແມ່ນພື້ນທີ່ສີ RGB ແບບຂະຫຍາຍ, ພັດທະນາໂດຍ Adobe. ມັນຖືກໃຊ້ສຳລັບແອັບພລິເຄຊັນການຖ່າຍຮູບ "
"ເຊັ່ນ: ການໂຄສະນາ ແລະ ງານສິລະປະ.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Wide "
"Gamut</emphasis>: ພື້ນທີ່ສີນີ້ແມ່ນເວີຊັນທີ່ຂະຫຍາຍຂອງພື້ນທີ່ສີ Adobe RGB.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Pro-Photo</emphasis>: ພື້ນທີ່ສີນີ້ແມ່ນພື້ນທີ່ສີ RGB, "
"ພັດທະນາໂດຍ Kodak, ທີ່ໃຫ້ຊ່ວງສີກວ້າງເປັນພິເສດ ອອກແບບມາສຳລັບໃຊ້ກັບຜົນລັດການຖ່າຍຮູບ.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Custom</emphasis>: ໃຊ້ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ພື້ນທີ່ສີຜົນລັດທີ່ກຳນົດເອງ.</item></list></para>"

