#: core/libs/tags/autoassignment/autotagsscanwidget.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid ""
"<p><b>This tool automatically assigns tags to images by analyzing the image using a deep-learning "
"neural network AI model.</b></p><p>The settings below configure the deep-learning AI model used for "
"analyzing image contents to identify objects. The AI neural network will automatically generate "
"descriptive tags for the image contents and store the results in the database.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p><b>ເຄື່ອງມືນີ້ຈະມອບໝາຍແທັກໃຫ້ຮູບພາບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດໂດຍການວິເຄາະຮູບພາບໂດຍໃຊ້ໂມເດລ AI deep-learning "
"neural network.</b></p><p>ການຕັ້ງຄ່າດ້ານລຸ່ມກຳນົດຄ່າໂມເດລ AI deep-learning ທີ່ໃຊ້ສຳລັບ "
"ວິເຄາະເນື້ອໃນຮູບພາບເພື່ອລະບຸວັດຖຸ. AI neural network ຈະສ້າງແທັກທີ່ອະທິບາຍເນື້ອໃນຮູບພາບ "
"ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ແລະ ບັນທຶກຜົນໄດ້ຮັບໄວ້ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ.</p>"

