#: core/utilities/import/main/importui.cpp:1245
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"There is not enough free space on the Camera Medium to upload pictures.\n"
"\n"
"Space require: %1\n"
"Available free space: %2"
msgstr ""
"ມີພື້ນທີ່ວ່າງບໍ່ພຽງພໍໃນສື່ຂອງກ້ອງເພື່ອອັບໂຫຼດຮູບພາບ.\n"
"\n"
"ພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ຕ້ອງການ: %1\n"
"ພື້ນທີ່ວ່າງທີ່ມີຢູ່: %2"

#: core/utilities/import/main/importui.cpp:1300
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Camera Folder \"%1\" already contains the item \"%2\".\n"
"Please enter a new filename (without extension):"
msgstr ""
"ໂຟນເດີກ້ອງ \"%1\" ມີລາຍການ \"%2\" ຢູ່ແລ້ວ.\n"
"ກະລຸນາປ້ອນຊື່ໄຟລ໌ໃໝ່ (ບໍ່ລວມນາມສະກຸນ):"

#: core/utilities/import/main/importui.cpp:1304
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "File Already Exists"
msgstr "ມີໄຟລ໌ຢູ່ແລ້ວ"

#: core/utilities/import/main/importui.cpp:1373
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Your custom target album date format is not valid. Please check your settings..."
msgstr "ຮູບແບບວັນທີຂອງອັນລະບັ້ມເປົ້າໝາຍທີ່ກຳນົດເອງບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງເຈົ້າ..."

#: core/utilities/import/main/importui.cpp:1413
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Collection which host your default target album set to process download from camera device is not "
"available. Please select another one from camera configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"ຄໍເລັກຊັນທີ່ໂຮດອັນລະບັ້ມເປົ້າໝາຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງເຈົ້າເພື່ອປະມວນຜົນການດາວໂຫຼດຈາກກ້ອງບໍ່ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ. "
"ກະລຸນາເລືອກອັນອື່ນຈາກກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບການຕັ້ງຄ່າກ້ອງ."

#: core/utilities/import/main/importui.cpp:1422
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Your default target album set to process download from camera device is not available. Please select "
"another one from camera configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"ອັນລະບັ້ມເປົ້າໝາຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງເຈົ້າເພື່ອປະມວນຜົນການດາວໂຫຼດຈາກກ້ອງບໍ່ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ. "
"ກະລຸນາເລືອກອັນອື່ນຈາກກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບການຕັ້ງຄ່າກ້ອງ."

#: core/utilities/import/main/importui.cpp:1447
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Please select the destination album from the digiKam library to import the camera pictures into."
msgstr "ກະລຸນາເລືອກອັນລະບັ້ມປາຍທາງຈາກຫໍສະໝຸດ digiKam ເພື່ອນຳເຂົ້າຮູບພາບຈາກກ້ອງ."

#: core/utilities/import/main/importui.cpp:1478
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Collection selected as the destination album to download from the camera device is not available. "
"Please select another destination album."
msgstr ""
"ຄໍເລັກຊັນທີ່ເລືອກເປັນອັນລະບັ້ມປາຍທາງເພື່ອດາວໂຫຼດຈາກກ້ອງບໍ່ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ. ກະລຸນາເລືອກອັນລະບັ້ມປາຍທາງອື່ນ."

