#: core/utilities/import/widgets/scriptingsettings.cpp:61
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>These expressions may be used to customize the command line:</p><p><b>%file</b>: full path of the "
"imported file</p><p><b>%filename</b>: file name of the imported file</p><p><b>%path</b>: path of the "
"imported file</p><p><b>%orgfilename</b>: original file name</p><p><b>%orgpath</b>: original path</"
"p><p>If there are no expressions full path is added to the command.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ນິພົດເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອປັບແຕ່ງແຖວຄຳສັ່ງ:</p><p><b>%file</b>: ເສັ້ນທາງເຕັມຂອງ "
"ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ນຳເຂົ້າ</p><p><b>%filename</b>: ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ນຳເຂົ້າ</p><p><b>%path</b>: ເສັ້ນທາງຂອງ "
"ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ນຳເຂົ້າ</p><p><b>%orgfilename</b>: ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບ</p><p><b>%orgpath</b>: ເສັ້ນທາງຕົ້ນສະບັບ</"
"p><p>ຖ້າບໍ່ມີນິພົດ, ເສັ້ນທາງເຕັມຈະຖືກເພີ່ມໃສ່ຄຳສັ່ງ.</p>"

