msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "ຂັ້ນສູງ"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:249
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"You should only activate this option if you are exchanging image metadata with programs that use the "
"sidecar format BASENAME.xmp. If you have images with the same base name (e.g. Image.CR2 and Image.JPG) "
"then the sidecar can no longer be uniquely assigned and will be used for both images, which can lead "
"to metadata problems."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຄວນເປີດໃຊ້ງານຕົວເລືອກນີ້ ກໍ່ຕໍ່ເມື່ອທ່ານກຳລັງແລກປ່ຽນ metadata ຂອງຮູບພາບກັບໂປຣແກຣມທີ່ໃຊ້ຮູບແບບ sidecar BASENAME.xmp. ຖ້າທ່ານມີຮູບພາບທີ່ມີຊື່ພື້ນຖານດຽວກັນ (ເຊັ່ນ Image.CR2 ແລະ Image.JPG) ດັ່ງນັ້ນ sidecar ຈະບໍ່ສາມາດຖືກກຳນົດໃຫ້ສະເພາະເຈາະຈົງໄດ້ ແລະ ຈະຖືກໃຊ້ສຳລັບທັງສອງຮູບພາບ, ເຊິ່ງອາດນຳໄປສູ່ບັນຫາ metadata ໄດ້."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:267
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Switching off exif auto rotation will most probably show your images in a wrong orientation, so only "
"change this option if you explicitly require this."
msgstr ""
"ການປິດການຫມຸນ exif ອັດຕະໂນມັດ ມັກຈະສະແດງຮູບພາບຂອງທ່ານໃນທິດທາງທີ່ຜິດ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນໃຫ້ປ່ຽນຕົວເລືອກນີ້ ກໍ່ຕໍ່ເມື່ອທ່ານຕ້ອງການແບບນີ້ແທ້ໆເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:290
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Do you really want to enable metadata writing to RAW files? digiKam delegates this task to the "
"ExifTool backend.\n"
"With different RAW formats, problems are known which can lead to the corrupt of RAW files.\n"
"If you decide to do so, make a backup of your RAW files. We strongly recommend not to enable this "
"option."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເປີດໃຊ້ງານການຂຽນ metadata ລົງໃນໄຟລ໌ RAW ແທ້ບໍ່? digiKam ມອບໝາຍໜ້າທີ່ນີ້ໃຫ້ກັບ ExifTool backend.\n"
"ດ້ວຍຮູບແບບ RAW ທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ, ມີບັນຫາທີ່ພົບເຫັນເຊິ່ງສາມາດນຳໄປສູ່ຄວາມເສຍຫາຍຂອງໄຟລ໌ RAW ໄດ້.\n"
"ຖ້າທ່ານຕັດສິນໃຈເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ສຳຮອງຂໍ້ມູນໄຟລ໌ RAW ຂອງທ່ານໄວ້. ພວກເຮົາຂໍແນະນຳຢ່າງແຂງແຮງວ່າຢ່າເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:298
#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:350
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Yes I Understand"
msgstr "ແມ່ນ ຂ້ອຍເຂົ້າໃຈ"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:308
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "You would rather disable writing metadata to RAW files?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຢາກປິດການຂຽນ metadata ລົງໃນໄຟລ໌ RAW ດີກວ່າບໍ່?"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:345
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"A RAW file extension has been added to the list of supported sidecars. There is a risk of accidentally "
"deleting RAW images. Are you sure you want to do that?"
msgstr ""
"ນາມສະກຸນໄຟລ໌ RAW ໄດ້ຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນລາຍຊື່ຂອງ sidecar ທີ່ຮອງຮັບແລ້ວ. ມີຄວາມສ່ຽງທີ່ຈະລຶບຮູບພາບ RAW ໂດຍບັງເອີນ. ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ວ່າຕ້ອງການເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ?"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:31
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option"
msgid "Baloo Desktop Search"
msgstr "ການຄົ້ນຫາເດັສທັອບ Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:35
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option"
msgid "Store metadata from digiKam in Baloo"
msgstr "ຈັດເກັບ metadata ຈາກ digiKam ໄວ້ໃນ Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:36
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Turn on this option to push rating, comments and tags from digiKam into the Baloo storage"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ເພື່ອສົ່ງການໃຫ້ຄະແນນ, ຄຳເຫັນ ແລະ ແທັກຈາກ digiKam ໄປຍັງບ່ອນຈັດເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຂອງ Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:40
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option"
msgid "Read metadata from Baloo"
msgstr "ອ່ານ metadata ຈາກ Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:41
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option if you want to apply changes to rating, comments and tags made in Baloo to "
"digiKam's metadata storage. Please note that image metadata will not be edited automatically."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງການໃຫ້ຄະແນນ, ຄຳເຫັນ ແລະ ແທັກທີ່ເຮັດໃນ Baloo ມາຍັງບ່ອນຈັດເກັບ metadata ຂອງ digiKam. ກະລຸນາຮັບຊາບວ່າ metadata ຂອງຮູບພາບຈະບໍ່ຖືກແກ້ໄຂໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:63
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"provides the basis to handle all kinds of metadata on the KDE desktop in a generic fashion. It allows "
"you to tag, rate and comment your files in KDE applications like Dolphin. Please set here if you want "
"to synchronize the metadata stored by digiKam desktop-wide with the Baloo Desktop Search."
msgstr ""
"ໃຫ້ພື້ນຖານໃນການຈັດການ metadata ທຸກປະເພດໃນເດັສທັອບ KDE ໃນຮູບແບບທົ່ວໄປ. ມັນອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ທ່ານແທັກ, ໃຫ້ຄະແນນ ແລະ ສະແດງຄຳເຫັນໃສ່ໄຟລ໌ຂອງທ່ານໃນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ KDE ເຊັ່ນ Dolphin. ກະລຸນາຕັ້ງຄ່າບ່ອນນີ້ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການຊິງຄ໌ metadata ທີ່ເກັບໄວ້ໂດຍ digiKam ໃຫ້ທົ່ວເດັສທັອບກັບ Baloo Desktop Search."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:84
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:tab"
msgid "Baloo"
msgstr "Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:34
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<para>In addition to the pixel content, image files usually contain a variety of metadata. A lot of "
"the parameters you can use in digiKam to manage files, such as rating or comment, can be written to "
"the files' metadata.</para> <para>Storing in metadata allows one to preserve this information when "
"moving or sending the files to different systems.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>ນອກເໜືອຈາກເນື້ອຫາຂອງພິກເຊວແລ້ວ, ໄຟລ໌ຮູບພາບມັກຈະມີ metadata ຫຼາກຫຼາຍ. ພາຣາມິເຕີຈຳນວນຫຼາຍທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ໃນ digiKam ເພື່ອຈັດການໄຟລ໌, ເຊັ່ນ: ການໃຫ້ຄະແນນ ຫຼື ຄຳເຫັນ, ສາມາດຂຽນລົງໃນ metadata ຂອງໄຟລ໌ໄດ້.</para> <para>ການຈັດເກັບໃນ metadata ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ສາມາດຮັກສາຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ໄວ້ໄດ້ ເມື່ອຍ້າຍ ຫຼື ສົ່ງໄຟລ໌ໄປຍັງລະບົບຕ່າງໆ.</para>"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:44
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Write This Information to the Metadata"
msgstr "ຂຽນຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ລົງໃນ Metadata"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:49
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Image tags"
msgstr "ແທັກຂອງຮູບພາບ"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:50
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid "Turn on this option to store the item tags in the XMP and IPTC tags."
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ເພື່ອຈັດເກັບແທັກຂອງລາຍການໄວ້ໃນແທັກ XMP ແລະ IPTC."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:54
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
