#: core/utilities/setup/setupdatabase.cpp:171
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"The process of updating the file hashes takes a few minutes or hours.\n"
"Please ensure that any important collections on removable media are connected.\n"
"After the upgrade you cannot use your database with a digiKam version prior to 8.5.0.\n"
"Do you want to begin the update?"
msgstr ""
"ຂັ້ນຕອນການອັບເດດ hash ຂອງໄຟລ໌ໃຊ້ເວລາສອງສາມນາທີ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍຊົ່ວໂມງ.\n"
"ກະລຸນາຮັບປະກັນວ່າຄໍເລັກຊັນທີ່ສຳຄັນໃດໆໃນສື່ທີ່ຖອດອອກໄດ້ຖືກເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຢູ່.\n"
"ຫຼັງຈາກການອັບເກຣດ ທ່ານຈະບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານກັບ digiKam ເວີຊັນກ່ອນ 8.5.0 ໄດ້.\n"
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນການອັບເດດບໍ່?"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupdatabase.cpp:185
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Updates"
msgstr "ການອັບເດດ"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupdatabase.cpp:188
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Update File Hashes"
msgstr "ອັບເດດ Hash ຂອງໄຟລ໌"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupdatabase.cpp:190
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"File hashes are used to identify identical files and to display thumbnails. A new, improved algorithm "
"to create the hash is now used. The old algorithm, though, still works quite well, so it is "
"recommended to carry out this upgrade, but not required.\n"
"After the upgrade you cannot use your database with a digiKam version prior to 8.5.0."
msgstr ""
"Hash ຂອງໄຟລ໌ຖືກໃຊ້ເພື່ອລະບຸໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຄືກັນ ແລະ ເພື່ອສະແດງຮູບຫຍໍ້. ຕອນນີ້ມີການໃຊ້ອະລັກກໍຣິດຶມໃໝ່ທີ່ປັບປຸງດີຂຶ້ນເພື່ອສ້າງ hash. ເຖິງຢ່າງໃດກໍ່ຕາມ, ອະລັກກໍຣິດຶມເກົ່າຍັງເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ດີພໍສົມຄວນ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນຈຶ່ງແນະນຳໃຫ້ດຳເນີນການອັບເກຣດນີ້, ແຕ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ບັງຄັບ.\n"
"ຫຼັງຈາກການອັບເກຣດ ທ່ານຈະບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານກັບ digiKam ເວີຊັນກ່ອນ 8.5.0 ໄດ້."

#: core/utilities/setup/setupdatabase.cpp:199
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Get information about <b>Update File Hashes</b>"
msgstr "ຮັບຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບ <b>ອັບເດດ Hash ຂອງໄຟລ໌</b>"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupgeolocation.cpp:106
#, kde-format
msgid "API Key:"
msgstr "ຄີ API:"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupgeolocation.cpp:117
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"To work friendly, Google Maps requires an API key that end users must buy online to gain credentials. "
"Without this key, Google Maps is still usable but with an overlay frame annotated \"For Development "
"Only\". For more information, see this <a href='https://mapsplatform.google.com/pricing/'>Google page</"
"a> about usages, practices, and prices."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ຢ່າງສະດວກ, Google Maps ຕ້ອງການຄີ API ທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຕ້ອງຊື້ອອນລາຍເພື່ອຮັບສິດ. ຖ້າບໍ່ມີຄີນີ້, Google Maps ຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ແຕ່ຈະມີກອບທັບຊ້ອນທີ່ຂຽນວ່າ \"For Development Only\" (ສຳລັບການພັດທະນາເທົ່ານັ້ນ). ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ, ເບິ່ງ <a href='https://mapsplatform.google.com/pricing/'>ໜ້າ Google</a> ນີ້ກ່ຽວກັບການນຳໃຊ້, ຂໍ້ປະຕິບັດ, ແລະ ລາຄາ."

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:139
#, kde-format
msgid "Enable Color Management"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ງານການຈັດການສີ"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:140
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<ul><li>Checked: Color Management is enabled</li><li>Unchecked: Color Management is disabled</li></ul>"
msgstr "<ul><li>ໝາຍຕິກ: ການຈັດການສີຖືກເປີດໃຊ້ງານ</li><li>ບໍ່ໝາຍຕິກ: ການຈັດການສີຖືກປິດໃຊ້ງານ</li></ul>"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:147
#, kde-format
msgid "Visit Little CMS project website"
msgstr "ເຂົ້າຊົມເວັບໄຊທ໌ໂຄງການ Little CMS"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:157
#, kde-format
msgid "Working Color Space"
msgstr "ພື້ນທີ່ສີໃນການເຮັດວຽກ"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:163
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>This is the color space all the images will be converted to when opened (if you choose to convert) "
"and the profile that will be embedded when saving. Good and safe choices are <b>Adobe RGB (1998)</b> "
"and <b>sRGB IEC61966-2.1</b></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ນີ້ແມ່ນພື້ນທີ່ສີທີ່ຮູບພາບທັງໝົດຈະຖືກແປງໄປຫາເມື່ອເປີດ (ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກທີ່ຈະແປງ) ແລະ ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຈະຖືກຝັງເມື່ອບັນທຶກ. ທາງເລືອກທີ່ດີ ແລະ ປອດໄພແມ່ນ <b>Adobe RGB (1998)</b> ແລະ <b>sRGB IEC61966-2.1</b></p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:169
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>You can use this button to get more detailed information about the selected workspace profile.</p>"
msgstr "<p>ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ປຸ່ມນີ້ເພື່ອຮັບຂໍ້ມູນລາຍລະອຽດເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກທີ່ເລືອກໄດ້.</p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:183
#, kde-format
msgid "When the profile of an image does not match the working color space"
msgstr "ເມື່ອໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຂອງຮູບພາບບໍ່ກົງກັບພື້ນທີ່ສີໃນການເຮັດວຽກ"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:191 core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:222
#, kde-format
msgid "Ask when opening the image"
msgstr "ຖາມເມື່ອເປີດຮູບພາບ"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:192
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>If an image has an embedded color profile not matching the working space profile, digiKam will ask "
"if you want to convert to the working space, keep the embedded profile or discard the embedded profile "
"and assign a different one.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ຖ້າຮູບພາບມີໂປຣໄຟລ໌ສີທີ່ຝັງຢູ່ບໍ່ກົງກັບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກ, digiKam ຈະຖາມວ່າທ່ານຕ້ອງການແປງໄປເປັນພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກ, ເກັບຮັກສາໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຝັງໄວ້ ຫຼື ຍົກເລີກໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຝັງໄວ້ ແລະ ກຳນົດອັນອື່ນໃຫ້.</p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:198
#, kde-format
msgid "Convert the image to the working color space"
msgstr "ແປງຮູບພາບໄປເປັນພື້ນທີ່ສີໃນການເຮັດວຽກ"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:199
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>If an image has an embedded color profile not matching the working space profile, digiKam will "
"convert the image's color information to the working color space. This changes the pixel data, but not "
"the appearance of the image.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ຖ້າຮູບພາບມີໂປຣໄຟລ໌ສີທີ່ຝັງຢູ່ບໍ່ກົງກັບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກ, digiKam ຈະແປງຂໍ້ມູນສີຂອງຮູບພາບໄປເປັນພື້ນທີ່ສີໃນການເຮັດວຽກ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະປ່ຽນຂໍ້ມູນພິກເຊວ, ແຕ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນລັກສະນະຂອງຮູບພາບ.</p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:215
#, kde-format
msgid "When an image has no color profile information"
msgstr "ເມື່ອຮູບພາບບໍ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ສີ"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:223
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>If an image has no embedded color profile, digiKam will ask which color space shall be used to "
"interpret the image and to which color space it shall be transformed for editing.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ຖ້າຮູບພາບບໍ່ມີໂປຣໄຟລ໌ສີທີ່ຝັງຢູ່, digiKam ຈະຖາມວ່າຄວນໃຊ້ພື້ນທີ່ສີໃດໃນການຕີຄວາມໝາຍຮູບພາບ ແລະ ຄວນແປງໄປເປັນພື້ນທີ່ສີໃດສຳລັບການແກ້ໄຂ.</p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:227
#, kde-format
msgid "Assume it is using the sRGB color space (Internet standard)"
msgstr "ສົມມຸດວ່າມັນກຳລັງໃຊ້ພື້ນທີ່ສີ sRGB (ມາດຕະຖານອິນເຕີເນັດ)"

#. i18n("<p></p>"));
#.
#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:233
#, kde-format
msgid "and convert it to the working color space"
msgstr "ແລະ ແປງມັນໄປເປັນພື້ນທີ່ສີໃນການເຮັດວຽກ"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:246
#, kde-format
msgid "Assume it is using the working color space"
msgstr "ສົມມຸດວ່າມັນກຳລັງໃຊ້ພື້ນທີ່ສີໃນການເຮັດວຽກ"

#. i18n("<p></p>"));
#.
#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:252
#, kde-format
msgid "Convert it from default input color space to working space"
msgstr "ແປງມັນຈາກພື້ນທີ່ສີ input ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໄປເປັນພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກ"

#: core/utilities/setup/setupicc.cpp:271
